<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Our App</title>
</head>
<body>
<p>Hello <strong>{{ user.email|e }}</strong>,</p>

<p>Welcome to our application! Please click the link below to validate your email address:</p>

<p>
    <a href="{{ validate_link }}" target="_blank" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px 15px; background-color: #0069d9; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;">
        Validate Your Email
    </a>
</p>

<p>This link will expire on <strong>{{ token_expiration|date('d-m-Y H:i') }}</strong>.</p>

<p>If you did not request this registration, you can ignore this email.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Team</p>
</body>
</html>
